data.text:
The headquarters building of Revco D.S., Inc. in Twinsburg, Ohio Thursday, Nov. 30, 1995. The nation's largest drugstore chain, Rite Aid Corp., announced a $1.8 million deal to buy Revco Thursday which would eliminate 1,100 jobs at the Revco Twinsburg headquarters. (AP Photo/Phil Long)
